1.0.name: wordpress/faq-you
1.0.description:
A simple FAQ plugin where you can create Categories and put Questions in them. You can easily insert them in a page with the WYSIWYG editor. Able to turn JavaScript on or off.

This plugin is designed to be easy for you and your clients. Easy for you to create a FAQ on a page, easy for the client to manage questions and categories.

Has a Dutch and English translation.
